GarminConnectr - Simple ruby lib to fetch data from Garmin Connect

The Garmin Connect API hasn't been released yet. This will suffice for now. 

Usage:

require 'garmin_connectr'
g = GarminConnectr.new( ACTIVITY_ID )
puts "#{ g.name } / #{ g.device } / #g{ }"


Methods:

name, url, device
start_time, start_time_str
activity, event, time, distance, calories
avg_speed, max_speed
elevation_gain, elevation_loss, min_elevation, max_elevation
avg_heartrate, max_heartrate
avg_cadence, max_cadence
avg_temperature, min_temperature, max_temperaute

Requires:
  Nokogiri